# gaia runtime + user-specific data — chat history, agent memory, sessions,
# recall/index dbs. Lives under a workspace's .gaia/ (or ~/.gaia, outside the
# repo). NEVER commit: it is per-user and often private.
.gaia/

# unmute runtime artifacts (the source is vendored; these are rebuilt locally)
unmute/.uv-cache/
unmute/.uv-python/
unmute/models/
